SUMMARY:Painting with Wool – 2D Needle Felted Scenery with Tamara Smith
DESCRIPTION:Students will make a 5” x 7” needle felted scene with clouds\, a tree and a barn. The instructor will provide all the supplies for the workshop. \nThis workshop is appropriate for beginners and intermediate level needle felters. \nFor more information or to register\, click here. \n\n           Download QR
